  <brief_title>Amount of Lactose Causing Symptoms in Lactose Intolerant People</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study to Determine the Threshold of Lactose Ingestion That Provokes Symptoms in Lactose Intolerant People.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
